      "date": "2016-03-22 07:19:23.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Verified-1\n\nTests uploaded by Trevis Autotest from trevis-10vm1 for review-dne-part-2 received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.7/x86_64: (https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sessions/4b7af672-effe-11e5-8202-5254006e85c2). Ran 15 tests.  2 tests failed: ost-pools, replay-single.",
